title: Social Media and Midwifery with Sheena Byrom OBE
desc: A collaborative event with City University London Midwifery Department, the Royal College of Midwives City & Hackney Branch and City University London Midwifery Society. Sheena Byrom OBE will present a seminar to explore Social Media and Midwifery. This event is open to City University midwifery students and members of the RCM City & Hackney branch.
